verbose_text: Immunohistochemical and immunofluorescent analysis of representative Daudi and SU-DHL-8 lymphoma xenograft samples showed colocalized CXCR4 and Ki67 expression patterns in the case of Daudi tumors, whereas CXCR4 expression and enhanced proliferation did not clearly correlate on a cellular level in the case of SU-DHL-8 tumors.
